choices.text: The Bills and Bengals will both be focused on playing their home games in the divisional round, as they have no chance of facing either Brady or Rodgers. Mahomes will be looking to lead the Chiefs to their fifth consecutive AFC title game.
Hamlin is back on his feet and that's uplifting enough for the Bills to focus on Sunday's playoff game against the Bengals.
The NFL is still a great sport with plenty of excitement this weekend.

Aryna Sabalenka improved her winning streak to six as she beat American Shelby Rogers 6-3, 6-1 on Thursday to reach the third round of the Australian Open. Sabalenka, who began the year by winning the title in Adelaide, trailed the American 3-1 early in the match but won five straight games to take the opening set and then eased through the second. Patrick Mahomes is one of the most creative and talented players in the NFL when it comes to playing in the postseason. His ability to make something out of nothing is what makes him so difficult to stop.
Dejounte Murray scored 30 points, Trae Young had 18 points and 12 assists, and the Atlanta Hawks beat the Dallas Mavericks 130-122.
